span style="line-height: 115%" unicode="">[sic]</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala; font-size: 14pt">&#4964; &#4808;&#4915;&#4915;&#4661;&#4752;&#4610;&#4961; &#4768;&#4707;&#4961; &#4635;&#4653;&#4678;&#4661;&#4961; &#4808;&#4824;&#4768;&#4925;&#4624;&#4936;&#4961; &#4768;&#4707;&#4961; &#4634;&#4779;&#4772;&#4621;&#4961; &#4808;&#4824;&#4920;&#4624;&#4936;&#4961; &#4773;&#4609;&#4737;&#4961; &#4634;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala; font-size: 14pt"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala; font-size: 14pt">&#4659;</span>&#4772;&#4621;&#4961; &#4824;&#4708;&#4720;&#4961; &#4768;&#4707;&#4961; &#4632;&#4899;&#4821;&#4964; &#4808;&#4676;&#4656;&#4961; &#4872;&#4704;&#4829;&#4610;&#4961; &#4720;&#4781;&#4616;&#4961; &#4635;&#4653;&#4843;&#4637;&#4961; &#4845;&#4925;&#4624;&#4941;&#4961; &#4661;&#4638;&#4633;&#4961; &#4736;&#4704;&#4961; &#4819;&#4637;&#4848;&#4961; &#4808;&#4653;&#4677;&#4961; &#4704;&#4672;&#4616;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala; font-size: 14pt"> </span><span style="line-height: 115%" unicode="">[sic]</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala; font-size: 14pt">&#4961; &#4925;&#4853;&#4677;&#4961; &#4768;&#4632;&#4961; &#4845;&#4632;&#4925;&#4773;&#4961; &#4781;&#4653;&#4661;&#4726;&#4661;&#4961; &#4618;&#4677;&#4961; &#4773;[&#4757;]&#4824;&#4961; &#4843;&#4853;&#4616;&#4672;&#4621;&#4677;&#4961; &#4704;&#4757;&#4901;&#4648;&#4961; &#4632;&#4707;&#4653;&#4677;&#4725;&#4961; &#4808;&#4704;&#4853;&#4621;&#4677;&#4621;&#4677;&#4962; &#4768;&#4636;&#4757;&#4962; &#4808;&#4768;&#4636;&#4757;&#4962;</span></p><foreign xml:lang="en"><p><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 10pt">Fol. 139vb: This Gospel book of &#704;abun&#228; Mamas of &#704;Ag&#228;rh&#601;&#347;e was written in the time of the reign of our King Tewoflos and of our Metropolitan &#704;abba Marqos. &#704;Abba Mika&#704;el caused it to&#160;be written, and his brother Misa&#704;el, of the house of &#704;abba M&#228;&#7789;a&#740;, wrote it. And the qes&#228; g&#228;b&#228;z (is) T&#228;kl&#228; Maryam. May </span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 10pt">Christ the Master write </span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 10pt">their names upon a pillar of gold in words of righteousness, when He comes instilling awe with the gleaming of thunderbolts and with shaking the earth. Amen and amen.</span></p></foreign>
